high_descs: Turn around then right to face the brown table.
Pick up the wooden spoon from the top of the table.
Turn right and walk forward towards the sink.
Place the spoon inside the sink and turn the faucet on, then turn it off and pick up the spoon.
Turn right and walk forward towards the sink.
Place the wooden spoon on top of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Wash the wooden spoon and place it on the counter of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the island
Pick up the turner on the island beside the bread
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the turner in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the turner then move to your right facing the counter
Put the turner on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the clean turner on the counter

high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the kitchen island.
Pick up the spatula on the kitchen island, the one to the right of the bread.
Turn right and go forward to the sink ahead.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the spatula on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the counter.
